Kyoon Tainu Main Dikhawan

Le Hun Din Vi Nai Chadya
Te Dil Ich Toon

Mere Man Ich Toon
Jadon Vi Nai Hondi Paas

Kadi Vi Na Jaway Door

Meri Jaan Kadi Vi Na Darein Mere Pyaare

Dil Ich Tu
Meri Hasrat Ae Toon

Assi Tere Ute Marde Ne, Sunde Nai Kyoon
Hun Te Roz Tainu Chaande Jaande

Ki Kariye Sajna Bol?

Tere Hi Jhool Ute Nachde Saare

Tere Ute Lakkhan Gaane Sone Jachde Ne
Dilan Di Yaari Saadi, Ve Dilan Da Naya Ae Qasoor

Naal Rehna Si Zaroor, Saade Te Arade
Mera Koi Aur Nai Ae Das Dita Duniya Nu

Jadon Vi Aave Apne Naal Laave Khushiyan Nu
Jadon Vi Door Jave, Jaan Saadi Kad Jave

Sajna Ae Tere Kol Wasna Ae Chaave
Muskura Ke Le Liti Ae Saadi Zimmawari

Nai Main Nai Kiti Kadi Vi Tere Toon Badgumani
Tu Mera Yaar Si, Dil Aasman Paar Si

Ae Do Dilan Da Pyaar Si Oh
Pyaar Na Si Kaaghazi Par

Meri Khwahish Ain Toon
Meri Hasrat Ain Toon

Hun Te Roz Tainu Chaande Jaande

Ki Kariye Sajna Bol

Tere Pyaar Ach Kariye Ki

Hun Bol, Sajna Kya Aawan Kol
Tere Te Main Wari Jawan

Tere Gun Gawan Main

Bas Tainu Chawan Main
